info: The Open Data Leaders Summit is an opportunity for individuals in government working in open data to learn from each other, and discuss strategies for achieving impact. Hear from leaders creating change in government from around the world and connect with peers sharing ideas, tools, networks and guides that can help you get more from your open data initiative.

session.description: The OD Leaders summit was an opportunity for individuals in government working in open data to learn from each other.

conference_notes: As final conclusions, the challenges that will be faced in the near future are information fragmentation; coordination and open licenses, as well as privacy concerns must be solved, but open data and LPT are a good opportunity to create value.
name: OD Leaders Summit: Getting to Impact
